    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0800b14"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>常州興寧寺<persName key="A010863">義宣</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0800b15"/><persName key="A010863">釋義宣</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000009723">晉陵</placeName>人也。宿<anchor xml:id="beg0800004"/>植<anchor xml:id="end0800004"/>利根，翛然出俗，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b16"/>不煩師訓，砥礪厥心。納法後，孜孜律科，時<lb
ed="T" n="0800b17"/>無虛度。玄儒旁綜，長在篇章，卒問捷給。而<lb
ed="T" n="0800b18"/>稟<ref type="person" target="#A019341">延陵</ref>恭讓之風，雅得毘尼之體。初<placeName key="PL000000010783">揚州</placeName><persName key="A009590">法<lb
ed="T" n="0800b19"/>慎</persName>傳<app type="multiplier" xml:id="begd1e25138"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e25138"/>舊章，<placeName key="PL000000000195">淮甸</placeName>之間，推為碩匠。<date from-iso="0742" key="j19921141993438" to-iso="0745">天寶初</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b20"/><persName key="A010863">宣</persName>斂衽摳衣，諮詢彌久，輩流率服。<persName key="A009590">慎</persName>且歎<lb
ed="T" n="0800b21"/>賞曰：「可畏乎！」<persName key="A010863">宣</persName>講<placeName key="PL000000042627">終南</placeName>《事鈔》，請業于<persName key="A011002">周律<lb
ed="T" n="0800b22"/>師</persName>之庭，考覈尤精，乃著《折中記》六卷以解<lb
ed="T" n="0800b23"/>之。蓋慊<persName key="A010829">融濟</persName>、<persName key="A010823">㠋</persName>、<persName key="A010930">勝</persName>諸師有所紕謬故也。<lb
ed="T" n="0800b24"/>使是非各盡其分，人免據宗而阿比，從此<lb
ed="T" n="0800b25"/>立稱耳。<placeName key="PL000000009739">毘陵</placeName>多出名士僧，有<persName key="G000024">三宣</persName>，<persName key="A011003">慧</persName>、<persName key="A009173">德</persName>、<persName key="A010863">義</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0800b26"/>是歟。時於<placeName key="PL000000010789">江都</placeName>習業，與<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName><persName key="A004177">曇一</persName>、閩川<persName key="A010861">懷<lb
ed="T" n="0800b27"/>一</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011901">慶雲</placeName><persName key="A009591">靈一</persName>同門為朋也。<placeName key="PL000000009723">晉陵</placeName>既有三宣，<lb
ed="T" n="0800b28"/><persName key="A009590">慎</persName>門復出<ref type="person" target="#A004177 #A010861 #A009591">三一</ref>焉。<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>資為美談。<persName key="A010863">宣</persName><date from-iso="0752" key="j19960861997410" to-iso="0756">天寶末</date><lb
ed="T" n="0800b29"/>盛行化導，罔究其終。</p><pb ed="T" n="0800c" xml:id="T50.2061.0800c"/>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0800c0101"><lb
ed="T" n="0800c01"/>系曰：夫名以制義，所出無窮，奈何師資踵<lb
ed="T" n="0800c02"/>武，而犯教祖之諱乎？通曰：「《春秋》貴賤不嫌<lb
ed="T" n="0800c03"/>同號也。」或曰：「滕齊不敵，俱書侯，乃曰不<lb
ed="T" n="0800c04"/>嫌同號。號與名豈得例諸？」通曰：「號大不<lb
ed="T" n="0800c05"/>嫌，名小豈嫌乎？矧以<persName key="A010863">義宣</persName>始為名者，安知<lb
ed="T" n="0800c06"/>弟子成事於<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>之門邪？然出家者必也無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c07"/>妨。一則姓既以華從梵，咸稱釋氏。一則<placeName key="PL000000055436">西<lb
ed="T" n="0800c08"/>域</placeName>無諱，此合從旃。<anchor xml:id="beg0800005"/>具<anchor xml:id="end0800005"/>諱者周人以事鬼<lb
ed="T" n="0800c09"/>神，夏商無諱明矣。況乎<persName key="A010863">宣師</persName>已生兜率，小<lb
ed="T" n="0800c10"/>為天人，大為菩薩，豈宜以鬼神事之？致<lb
ed="T" n="0800c11"/>令<date from-iso="0618" key="j19469511973336" to-iso="0690">唐初</date>高德<persName key="A010930">勝士</persName>，往往止存一字名，職由諱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c12"/>之極矣。屬今修撰，乃闕文也。乃知真諦無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c13"/>諱，俗諦聞似則懼。」或曰：「今沙門姓既為釋，<lb
ed="T" n="0800c14"/>名復不諱，言我不隨俗諦，云何對君主稱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c15"/>臣？莫<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>有否？」通曰：「姓名不對王者，臣<lb
ed="T" n="0800c16"/>妾表疏合然。昔齊帝問<persName key="A003052">王儉</persName>，遂令對見稱<lb
ed="T" n="0800c17"/>名。自<date from-iso="0023" key="j17295281999510" to-iso="0762">漢至唐肅宗朝</date>，始見稱臣，由此沿<lb
ed="T" n="0800c18"/>而不革。良以沙門德薄，日就衰微，一往無<lb
ed="T" n="0800c19"/>復矣。又以法委國王，誠難改作。王謂為是，<lb
ed="T" n="0800c20"/>楷定莫移。故佛言雖非我制，諸方為清淨<lb
ed="T" n="0800c21"/>者，不得不行也。」</p>
